                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-01-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Commanders of Spanish naval ships and of German training ship have called upon
                    commander of <hi rend="italic">Maine</hi> and their visits will be returned
                    afternoon. Salutes exchanged. All quiet.</p>
            </div>
